images.alt: A highly detailed digital anime illustration in the style of Attack on Titan, featuring a young teenage boy with short dark hair viewed from behind, standing confidently on a rooftop edge with legs apart, wearing a brown hooded jacket emblazoned with blue and white wings of freedom emblem on the back, blue pants, black boots, and dual 3D maneuver gear holsters on his hips with gas tanks and blades. Below, a sprawling futuristic cityscape at dusk, buildings illuminated in warm orange glow, surrounded by billowing yellow-orange clouds and mist. High contrast, dynamic lighting with god rays from the titan, detailed textures on skin, clouds, and city lights. Cinematic wide-angle lens, depth of field focusing on the boy and titan, background slightly blurred. Art style: hyper-realistic anime with painterly brush strokes, inspired by Studio Wit and fan art, 8k resolution, vertical wallpaper format.
